headline: Xcel Energy Elects Maria Demaree to Board of Directors
summary: MINNEAPOLIS, December 17, 2025--Xcel Energy Inc. (NASDAQ: XEL) announced today that Maria Demaree has been elected to its board of directors, effective December 17, 2025.

headline: Xcel Energy Inc. Board Declares Dividend on Common Stock
summary: MINNEAPOLIS, December 17, 2025--The Board of Directors of Xcel Energy Inc. (NASDAQ: XEL) today declared a quarterly dividend on its common stock of 57 cents per share. The dividends are payable January 20, 2026, to shareholders of record on December 29, 2025.

headline: Assessing Xcel Energy’s Valuation After Recent Pullback and Grid Modernization Push
summary: If you are wondering whether Xcel Energy at around $73.73 is a solid entry point or already priced for perfection, you are in the right place to unpack what the market is really implying about its value. Despite being up 10.3% year to date and 11.9% over the last year, the stock has pulled back recently, slipping 2.6% over the past week and 8.5% across the last month, which can sometimes open up a more interesting risk reward setup for long term investors.
